'''Onie Arkmen''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Homeworld/Legends|native]] [[Coruscanti/Legends|to]]<ref name="Databank" /> the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]<ref name="Chronicles">''[[Star Wars Chronicles: The Prequels]]''</ref> [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. She was a partygoer<ref name="Databank" /> who participated in her homeworld's party scene.<ref name="Rogues Gallery" /> Arkmen was present in the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]] when [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] were seeking [[Zam Wesell/Legends|Zam Wesell]].<ref name="AOTC">{{Film|II}}</ref> She was scarcely dressed with small silver shorts, a small chain-mail top, and golden high heels, and wore an elaborate hairstyle and dark makeup.<ref name="Databank" /><ref name="Rogues Gallery">{{InsiderCite|136|Rogues Gallery|Rogues Gallery: A Night at the Outlander Club}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The actress playing Arkmen, in costume, introduced the thirteenth episode of the [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|Episode II]] behind-the-scenes video series [[On location|''on location'']].<ref name="On location">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/onloc/13.html|series=On Location|text=Part 13 - Ready for my Digital Close-Up}}</ref>

